Business Brief -- Marsh  McLennan Cos.:
   European Offices Realigned,
   Including New Acquisitions
Roland Seul, managing director in Munich, was named
chairman of Marsh  McLennan Europe. The unit's board
includes about a dozen senior operating officers from the
various countries.
   Marsh  McLennan Europe reports to David D. Holbrook,
president of Marsh  McLennan Inc., a major subsidiary of
Marsh  McLennan Cos., of New York. He said the new unit
"recognizes how clients are going to be operating in the
European Community." With recent acquisitions, he added, "we
are positioned exactly where we wanted to be."